{SOUTH bids 3\S to show a strong hand with a singleton \S. 

After NORTH shows her first-round \C control SOUTH decides he will bid slam if NORTH has three Aces.

When Blackwood reveals just two Aces in NORTH, SOUTH stops at 5\H.}

